==========================================================================="
"Software required to compile program:"
"=========================================================================="
"1. C/C++ compiler/linker"
"2. Any Message Passing Interface (MPI) implementation"
"3. GNU Scientific Library (GSL)"
"4. Portable Extensible Toolkit for Scientific Computation (PetSc) libraries"
"5. Scalable Linear Eigenvalue Problem Computation (Slepc) libraries"
"=========================================================================="
"Software recommended for debugging"
"=========================================================================="
"Valgrind with MPI wrapper library"
"=========================================================================="
